        "Topic": "Lines and Angles: Properties derived from intersecting lines.",
        "Description": "This topic covers the angle relationships formed when two lines intersect: vertically opposite angles (which are equal) and adjacent angles that form a linear pair (which sum to 180\u00b0)."
